o Mocks / Moq) Unit Testing Frameworks (NUnit / MSTest) Multithreading   DesiredSkills Lucene.NET Windows Workflow Foundation (WF) ServiceStack WatiN MS Visual C++ Cloud Services experience e.g Amazon Web Services, Windows Azure Video and Audio transcoding experience.   Tools Visual Studio 2012/13 SQL Server Management Studio Internet Information Services (IIS) Manager TeamCity ReSharper dotCoverAbout this companyIMDWe are the World's #1 TV commercial distribution specialist. Aiming to make video content distribution as simple as email, IMD’s elegant and powerful “Software as a Service” cloud-based solution is available to senders in any part of the Internet-enabled world at any time. IMD’s client base ranges over the entire media ecosphere; advertisers, production and post-production, creative and media agencies, content creators, web publishers, TV broadcasters and online marketers. The combination of automated content checking at source and rapid delivery processing means that IMD is at the very leading edge of distribution technology, establishing an enviable reputation for speed, reliability and service. This results in flexibility, increased speed, efficiency and reliability; higher quality delivery that is both dependable and cost efficient; and environmental impact reductions of more than 95%.Similar jobsSingaporePosted 7 days agoSingaporePosted 28 days agoSingaporePosted 20 days agoSingaporePosted 18 days agoSingaporePosted 13 days agoSingaporePosted 6 days agoSingaporePosted 10 days agoSingaporePosted 13 days agoKitchener, Canada AreaPosted 28 days agoGreater Atlanta AreaPosted 19 days agoThis is a preview of the Senior Software Developer job at IMD. To view the full job listing, join LinkedIn - its free!Join LinkedIn - its free!People also searchedPeople also viewedSingaporePosted 6 days agoSingaporePosted 7 days agoSingaporePosted 7 days agoSingaporePosted 6 days agoSingaporePosted 10 days agoSingaporePosted 7 days agoSingaporePosted 8 days agoSingaporeP